  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "NHKの人気子供番組「おかあさんといっしょ」のキャラクター「にこにこぷん」をフィーチャーしたゲームです。じゃじゃまる、ぴっころ、ぽろりの3人のキャラクターと一緒に様々なミニゲームを楽しめます。",
      "lang": "ja",
      "source": "romu"
    },
    {
      "text": "Jajamaru, Pikkoro and Porori one day arrive on an island where they find a cute little pink dragon. The poor thing is starving and they all decide to help him and escort the animal through several stages to collect his favorite food (displayed at the bottom of the screen).",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb"
    }
  ],
